Angular with Inifinite Scroll that pull data from Wordpress Json API

to run,
-----
install:
compass, sass, node 8+ w/ npm, bower

run
 1) bower install
 2) npm install
 3) grunt serve

it will open a browser and start the website
all changes update browser automatically

file structure
-------------
all styles are in main.scss under app/styles
index.html uses main.html view as main and only view.

